    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A coarse-grained igneous rock, largely granite, sometimes rich in rare elements such as uranium, tungsten, and tantalum.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
